org.bff.javampd.artist

Class MPDArtistDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bff.javampd.artist.MPDArtistDatabase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ArtistDatabase

    public class MPDArtistDatabase
extends Object
implements ArtistDatabase
    MPDArtistDatabase represents a artist database controller to a MPD. To obtain an instance of the class you must use the MusicDatabase.getArtistDatabase() method from the MPD connection class.
    Author:
    Bill
